---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /index.html
title: 'BlitzBlank — Premium Reinigung in Düsseldorf'
description: 'Ausgezeichnete Reinigungsmanufaktur, der über 500 Kunden vertrauen. Büro-, Privat-, Industrie- und Tiefenreinigung mit liebevoller Sorgfalt. 100% Zufriedenheitsgarantie.'
robots: 'index, follow'
navbarSolid: false
---
  <main id="main">
    <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
    <section class="hero" aria-label="Hero">
      <div class="hero__bg" aria-hidden="true">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154340-be6161a56a0c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80"
             alt=""
             loading="eager"
             fetchpriority="high" />
      </div>
      <div class="hero__overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <!-- Decorative floating blobs for richer glass effect -->
      <div class="blob blob--blue" style="width: 480px; height: 480px; top: -120px; left: -120px;" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="blob blob--cyan" style="width: 400px; height: 400px; bottom: -80px; right: -80px;" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="hero__content">
        <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--light hero__eyebrow">
          <span class="eyebrow__dot"></span>
          <span data-i18n="hero.eyebrow">Trusted by 500+ Düsseldorf clients</span>
        </span>

        <h1 class="hero__title">
          <span class="hero-line hero-line--1" data-i18n="hero.title1">Immaculate spaces,</span><br />
          <span class="hero-line hero-line--2" data-i18n="hero.title2">crafted with</span>
          <span class="hero-line hero-line--3 text-gradient" data-i18n="hero.title3">obsessive care.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="hero__subtitle" data-i18n="hero.subtitle">
          We are BlitzBlank — a boutique cleaning studio delivering five-star residential and commercial cleaning across Düsseldorf. Spotless results, every visit, guaranteed in writing.
        </p>

        <div class="hero__cta">
          <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" data-magnetic>
            <span data-i18n="hero.cta1">Book a Free Walkthrough</span>
            <svg class="icon icon--arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="services.html" class="btn btn--ghost-light btn--lg"><span data-i18n="hero.cta2">Explore Services</span></a>
        </div>

        <div class="hero__stats">
          <div class="hero__stat">
            <div class="hero__stat-num"><span data-counter="500" data-suffix="+">0</span></div>
            <div class="hero__stat-label" data-i18n="hero.stat1.label">Happy Clients</div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero__stat">
            <div class="hero__stat-num"><span data-counter="15" data-suffix="+">0</span></div>
            <div class="hero__stat-label" data-i18n="hero.stat2.label">Years Experience</div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero__stat">
            <div class="hero__stat-num"><span data-counter="100" data-suffix="%">0</span></div>
            <div class="hero__stat-label" data-i18n="hero.stat3.label">Satisfaction</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="#stats" class="scroll-indicator" aria-label="Scroll down">
        <span data-i18n="hero.scroll">Scroll</span>
        <span class="scroll-indicator__mouse" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </a>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== STRIP / Marquee ===== -->
    <div class="strip" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="marquee">
        <div class="marquee__track">
          <span class="strip__item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> <span data-i18n="strip.1">Eco-Friendly Products</span></span>
          <span class="strip__item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> <span data-i18n="strip.2">Background-Checked Crews</span></span>
          <span class="strip__item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> <span data-i18n="strip.3">100% Satisfaction Guarantee</span></span>
          <span class="strip__item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> <span data-i18n="strip.4">Same-Day Availability</span></span>
          <span class="strip__item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> <span data-i18n="strip.5">Insured & Bonded</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="marquee__track" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="strip__item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> <span data-i18n="strip.1">Eco-Friendly Products</span></span>
          <span class="strip__item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> <span data-i18n="strip.2">Background-Checked Crews</span></span>
          <span class="strip__item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> <span data-i18n="strip.3">100% Satisfaction Guarantee</span></span>
          <span class="strip__item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> <span data-i18n="strip.4">Same-Day Availability</span></span>
          <span class="strip__item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> <span data-i18n="strip.5">Insured & Bonded</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== STATS ===== -->
    <section class="section section--gradient" id="stats" aria-label="Our impact in numbers">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <span class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span> <span data-i18n="stats.eyebrow">By the Numbers</span></span>
          <h2 class="section-title" data-i18n="stats.title">A track record you can trust</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle" data-i18n="stats.subtitle">Fifteen years. Thousands of spotless rooms. A reputation earned one detail at a time.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="stats-grid" data-stagger="120">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-card__num"><span data-counter="500" data-suffix="+">0</span></span>
            <span class="stat-card__label" data-i18n="stats.1.label">Happy Clients</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-card__num"><span data-counter="12500" data-suffix="+">0</span></span>
            <span class="stat-card__label" data-i18n="stats.2.label">Cleans Completed</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-card__num"><span data-counter="15" data-suffix="+">0</span></span>
            <span class="stat-card__label" data-i18n="stats.3.label">Years Experience</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-card__num"><span data-counter="100" data-suffix="%">0</span></span>
            <span class="stat-card__label" data-i18n="stats.4.label">Satisfaction</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== SERVICES ===== -->
    <section class="section" id="services" aria-label="Our services">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <span class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span> <span data-i18n="services.eyebrow">What We Do</span></span>
          <h2 class="section-title" data-i18n="services.title">Cleaning services for every space</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle" data-i18n="services.subtitle">From boutique offices to sprawling warehouses, we bring the same obsessive attention to detail to every job we touch.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="services-grid" data-stagger="100">
          {% set variant = 'home' %}
          {% for service in services | selectattr('onHome') | sort(attribute='homeOrder') %}
          {% include "partials/service-card.njk" %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>

        <div style="text-align:center; margin-top: var(--space-12);" data-reveal>
          <a href="services.html" class="btn btn--outline btn--lg"><span data-i18n="services.viewAll">View all 10 services</span>
            <svg class="icon icon--arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== ABOUT PREVIEW ===== -->
    <section class="section section--tinted" id="about-preview" aria-label="About BlitzBlank">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-preview">
          <div class="about-preview__media" data-reveal="left">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1527515637462-cff94eecc1ac?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
                 alt="BlitzBlank team member in uniform preparing cleaning supplies"
                 loading="lazy" />
            <div class="about-preview__badge">
              <span class="about-preview__badge-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2 L15 8 L22 9 L17 14 L18 21 L12 17 L6 21 L7 14 L2 9 L9 8 Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg>
              </span>
              <div>
                <div class="about-preview__badge-num">4.9 / 5.0</div>
                <div class="about-preview__badge-text" data-i18n="about.badge">Average rating from 528 verified reviews</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="about-preview__content" data-reveal="right">
            <span class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span> <span data-i18n="about.eyebrow">Our Story</span></span>
            <h2 style="margin-top: var(--space-4)" data-i18n="about.title">A boutique studio, not a faceless franchise.</h2>
            <p data-i18n="about.desc">Founded in 2010 in a single Düsseldorf apartment, BlitzBlank has grown into the Rhine-Ruhr region's most quietly trusted cleaning studio. We refuse to franchise. Every crew is hired, trained, and equipped in-house — because quality is something you can't outsource.</p>

            <div class="about-preview__grid">
              <div class="about-preview__item">
                <h4 data-i18n="about.f1.title">Vetted Crews</h4>
                <p data-i18n="about.f1.desc">Background-checked, uniformed, and trained for 80 hours before stepping into your space.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="about-preview__item">
                <h4 data-i18n="about.f2.title">Eco-First</h4>
                <p data-i18n="about.f2.desc">Plant-based, pH-neutral products that are safe for kids, pets, and the planet.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="about-preview__item">
                <h4 data-i18n="about.f3.title">Real Guarantee</h4>
                <p data-i18n="about.f3.desc">Not happy with a clean? We return within 24 hours to make it right, free.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="about-preview__item">
                <h4 data-i18n="about.f4.title">Transparent Pricing</h4>
                <p data-i18n="about.f4.desc">Flat-rate quotes online in 60 seconds. No surprises, no upsells, no nickel-and-diming.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <a href="about.html" class="btn btn--dark"><span data-i18n="about.cta">Meet the team</span>
              <svg class="icon icon--arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== GALLERY PREVIEW ===== -->
    <section class="section" id="gallery-preview" aria-label="Gallery preview">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <span class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span> <span data-i18n="gallery.eyebrow">Recent Work</span></span>
          <h2 class="section-title" data-i18n="gallery.title">Spaces we've transformed</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle" data-i18n="gallery.subtitle">A glimpse into the rooms, offices, and venues we've recently brought back to life.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="masonry" data-stagger="80">
          <div class="masonry__item">
            <img class="masonry__img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581578731548-c64695cc6952?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Spotless modern kitchen after deep cleaning" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="masonry__overlay">
              <span class="masonry__cat" data-i18n="gallery.cat1">Residential</span>
              <span class="masonry__title" data-i18n="gallery.title1">Modern Kitchen Reset</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="masonry__item">
            <img class="masonry__img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366216548-37526070297c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Bright open-plan office space freshly cleaned" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="masonry__overlay">
              <span class="masonry__cat" data-i18n="gallery.cat2">Commercial</span>
              <span class="masonry__title" data-i18n="gallery.title2">Open-Plan Office</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="masonry__item">
            <img class="masonry__img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586023492125-27b2c045efd7?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Minimalist living room with natural light" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="masonry__overlay">
              <span class="masonry__cat" data-i18n="gallery.cat1">Residential</span>
              <span class="masonry__title" data-i18n="gallery.title3">Sunlit Living Room</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="masonry__item">
            <img class="masonry__img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554995207-c18c203602cb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Clean corporate workspace" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="masonry__overlay">
              <span class="masonry__cat" data-i18n="gallery.cat2">Commercial</span>
              <span class="masonry__title" data-i18n="gallery.title4">Corporate Suite</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="masonry__item">
            <img class="masonry__img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1567548083313-04c67ac2f4f0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Sparkling bathroom with chrome fixtures" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="masonry__overlay">
              <span class="masonry__cat" data-i18n="gallery.cat3">Deep Clean</span>
              <span class="masonry__title" data-i18n="gallery.title5">Spa-Grade Bathroom</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="masonry__item">
            <img class="masonry__img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366754035-f200968a6e72?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Modern conference room" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="masonry__overlay">
              <span class="masonry__cat" data-i18n="gallery.cat2">Commercial</span>
              <span class="masonry__title" data-i18n="gallery.title6">Boardroom Refresh</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="masonry__item">
            <img class="masonry__img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1484101403633-562f891dc89a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Polished hardwood floors" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="masonry__overlay">
              <span class="masonry__cat" data-i18n="gallery.cat4">Floor Care</span>
              <span class="masonry__title" data-i18n="gallery.title7">Hardwood Revival</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="masonry__item">
            <img class="masonry__img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1631679706909-1844bbd07221?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Modern dining area" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="masonry__overlay">
              <span class="masonry__cat" data-i18n="gallery.cat5">Hospitality</span>
              <span class="masonry__title" data-i18n="gallery.title8">Restaurant Dining</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align:center; margin-top: var(--space-12);" data-reveal>
          <a href="gallery.html" class="btn btn--outline btn--lg"><span data-i18n="gallery.cta">View full gallery</span>
            <svg class="icon icon--arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== TESTIMONIALS ===== -->
    <section class="section section--dark" id="reviews" aria-label="Customer reviews">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--light"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span> <span data-i18n="testimonials.eyebrow">Client Stories</span></span>
          <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--color-white)" data-i18n="testimonials.title">Loved by 500+ Düsseldorf clients</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" data-i18n="testimonials.subtitle">A few of the kind words we've collected over the years.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="slider" data-autoplay="true" data-interval="6000" data-reveal>
          <div class="slider__track">
            {% for testimonial in testimonials %}
            <div class="slider__slide">
              <div class="testimonial">
                <div class="testimonial__rating" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2 L15 8 L22 9 L17 14 L18 21 L12 17 L6 21 L7 14 L2 9 L9 8 Z"/></svg>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2 L15 8 L22 9 L17 14 L18 21 L12 17 L6 21 L7 14 L2 9 L9 8 Z"/></svg>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2 L15 8 L22 9 L17 14 L18 21 L12 17 L6 21 L7 14 L2 9 L9 8 Z"/></svg>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2 L15 8 L22 9 L17 14 L18 21 L12 17 L6 21 L7 14 L2 9 L9 8 Z"/></svg>
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2 L15 8 L22 9 L17 14 L18 21 L12 17 L6 21 L7 14 L2 9 L9 8 Z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <p class="testimonial__text" data-i18n="review.{{ loop.index }}.text">{{ testimonial.quote }}</p>
                <div class="testimonial__author">
                  <img class="testimonial__avatar" src="{{ testimonial.avatar }}" alt="Portrait of {{ testimonial.name }}" loading="lazy" />
                  <div>
                    <div class="testimonial__name" data-i18n="review.{{ loop.index }}.name">{{ testimonial.name }}</div>
                    <div class="testimonial__role" data-i18n="review.{{ loop.index }}.role">{{ testimonial.role }}</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>

          <div class="slider__controls">
            <button class="slider__btn slider__btn--prev" aria-label="Previous testimonial">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="slider__dots" role="tablist" aria-label="Choose testimonial">
              <button class="slider__dot" role="tab" aria-label="Testimonial 1"></button>
              <button class="slider__dot" role="tab" aria-label="Testimonial 2"></button>
              <button class="slider__dot" role="tab" aria-label="Testimonial 3"></button>
              <button class="slider__dot" role="tab" aria-label="Testimonial 4"></button>
            </div>
            <button class="slider__btn slider__btn--next" aria-label="Next testimonial">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Brand logos -->
        <div class="brands" data-reveal style="justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: var(--space-16)">
          <span class="brands__item">Northwind</span>
          <span class="brands__item">Maison Verde</span>
          <span class="brands__item">Rheinland</span>
          <span class="brands__item">Atlas Lofts</span>
          <span class="brands__item">Veritas Co.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== FAQ ===== -->
    <section class="section section--tinted" id="faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <span class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span> <span data-i18n="faq.eyebrow">Good to Know</span></span>
          <h2 class="section-title" data-i18n="faq.title">Frequently asked questions</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle" data-i18n="faq.subtitle">Everything you need to know before booking. Still curious? Just reach out — we love to chat.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-wrap" data-reveal>
          {% for item in faq %}
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" type="button">
              <span data-i18n="faq.{{ loop.index }}.q">{{ item.q }}</span>
              <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
              </span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <div class="faq-answer__inner" data-i18n="faq.{{ loop.index }}.a">
                {{ item.a }}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== CONTACT CTA ===== -->
    <section class="section" id="contact-cta" aria-label="Get in touch">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="promo-banner" data-reveal>
          <div class="promo-banner__content">
            <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--light" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-5)"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span> <span data-i18n="cta.eyebrow">Ready When You Are</span></span>
            <h2 data-i18n="cta.title">Let's make your space immaculate.</h2>
            <p data-i18n="cta.desc">Get a personalised quote in under 60 seconds. No obligations, no pressure — just a real conversation about what your space needs.</p>
            <div class="hero__cta" style="justify-content: center; opacity: 1; animation: none;">
